<br></span></p><p class="sc-fPrdjK bLmLvT pf-201_" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-6c9ba47b-25c1-4c90-99d8-c86777f4f13d"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">If your organisation still relies on manual training systems, now is the time to ask:
